$pearl_page_beauty["about-us"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][stm_sidebar sidebar="1064"][/vc_column][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-9 vc_col-md-9"][stm_spacer height_tablet="60" height_mobile="50"][vc_single_image image="1434" img_size="full" alignment="center"][vc_custom_heading text="We are the best" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]For something as fun as makeup, it tends to be at the center of a lot of controversy. Women who choose to wear it are sometimes accused of “lying,” while others are viewed as lacking confidence. It’s a sad reality, but these kinds of accusations often shame ladies from layering on the foundation and mascara that might make them feel a bit better about themselves in the morning (or that they just straight-up love). Beauty vlogger NikkieTutorials is here to set the haters straight, BuzzFeed reports. “I’ve been noticing a lot lately that girls have been almost ashamed to say they love makeup,” Nikkie states in the beginning of the video above. “Because, nowadays, when you say you love makeup, you either do it because you want to look good for boys, you do it because you’re insecure, or you do it because you don’t love yourself. I feel like, in a way, lately, it’s almost a crime to love doing your makeup.”[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="Our mission" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]It’s a sad reality, but these kinds of accusations often shame ladies from layering on the foundation and mascara that might make them feel a bit better about themselves in the morning (or that they just straight-up love).[/vc_column_text][stm_iconlist icon_color="stc" icon="fa fa-check-square" iconsize="14"] <ul> <li>We guarantee our customers are receiving the very best</li> <li>We offer hands on treatments with friendly</li> <li>We would love to welcome you to our salon</li> </ul> [/stm_iconlist][stm_spacer height="70" height_tablet="40" height_mobile="30"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1496814124150{margin-bottom: -60px !important;background: #63bac1 url(http://pearl.stylemixthemes.com/beauty/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2017/05/beauty_pattern.png?id=66) !important;}"][vc_column][stm_cta button_color="white" button_icon_pos="" style="style_4" link="url:%2Fbeauty%2Freservation%2F|title:Book%20your%20visit||" css=".vc_custom_1496839146546{background-position: 0 0 !important;background-repeat: repeat !important;}"]Book your visit online and save 10%[/stm_cta][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'meta' => array ( '_vc_post_settings' => array ( 0 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', ), '_edit_lock' => array ( 0 => '1501764575:1', ), '_edit_last' => array ( 0 => '1', ), '_wp_page_template' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), 'slide_template' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), '_wpb_vc_js_status' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'page_title_breadcrumbs' => array ( 0 => '', ), 'page_title_box' => array ( 0 => '', ), 'page_title_box_align' => array ( 0 => 'left', ), 'page_title_box_title_size' => array ( 0 => 'h2', ), 'page_title_box_bg_color' => array ( 0 => 'rgb(92, 55, 62)', ), 'page_title_box_text_color' => array ( 0 => 'ffffff', ), 'page_title_box_line_color' => array ( 0 => 'ffffff', ), 'page_title_box_subtitle_color' => array ( 0 => 'ffffff', ), 'page_title_button_text' => array ( 0 => 'Get in touch', ), 'page_title_button_url' => array ( 0 => '/construction/contact-us', ), 'stm_sidebar_position' => array ( 0 => 'left', ), 'ampforwp-amp-on-off' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), 'ampforwp_custom_content_editor' => array ( 0 => '', ), 'ampforwp_custom_content_editor_checkbox' => array ( 0 => '', ), '_wpb_shortcodes_custom_css' => array ( 0 => '.vc_custom_1496814124150{margin-bottom: -60px !important;background: #63bac1 url(http://pearl.stylemixthemes.com/beauty/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2017/05/beauty_pattern.png?id=66) !important;}.vc_custom_1496839146546{background-position: 0 0 !important;background-repeat: repeat !important;}', ), ), );
$pearl_page_beauty["were-hiring"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][stm_sidebar sidebar="1064"][/vc_column][vc_column el_class="right_column" offset="vc_col-lg-9 vc_col-md-9"][vc_custom_heading text="Wanna Work for Beauty Industry? We need You!" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]For something as fun as makeup, it tends to be at the center of a lot of controversy. Women who choose to wear it are sometimes accused of “lying,” while others are viewed as lacking confidence. It’s a sad reality, but these kinds of accusations often shame ladies from layering on the foundation and mascara that might make them feel a bit better about themselves in the morning (or that they just straight-up love).[/vc_column_text][vc_tta_accordion c_icon="triangle" active_section="1" autoplay="5" style="" shape="" color="" spacing="" gap="" c_align="" c_position="" css=".vc_custom_1490675647650{margin-bottom: 39px !important;}"][vc_tta_section title="Health and Wellness" tab_id="1490617357592-03169659-0e69"][vc_column_text] <div class="vc_tta-panel-heading">Staying fit and healthy is not a fad that will be forgotten by next year. The reasons for the trend towards healthy lifestyles have always been easy to understand, but only now are we beginning to see the significance of this trend and the long term impact it has on us as individuals.</div> [/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Beauty salon benefits" tab_id="1490617357634-7e87b5b9-5435"][vc_column_text]A regular visit to the beauty salon is no longer a luxury. For many women &amp; some men juggling work and home can be very time to consume and at times stressful.  A professional beauty salon needs to be able to offer a comprehensive range of skin care treatments, provide effective home care product solutions which suit your skin type and condition and a place to relax, unwind, throw away your cares for a while.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Employee-paid benefits" tab_id="1490617423595-a7ae1492-64d5"][vc_column_text]Employers know that the more benefits they can offer to their employees, the more likely the employees will not walk out on the job, leaving them in a bind. Employee turn over can be a real expensive problem for employers today because of training expenses, human resource manpower, and other tasks.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Trainings &amp; development" tab_id="1490617428207-db35e79e-76fa"][vc_column_text]Training and development is always acknowledged as crucial to the success of any business. Conversely, it is often the first area to feel the cutbacks when times are hard. As a busy executive, it can be challenging to balance the responsibility for developing your team with reducing budgets and focusing on the bottom line.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="High-class customer service" tab_id="1495689689957-25ef1262-fe9f"][vc_column_text]In the world of customer service, perception can mean the difference between a good or bad customer service experience. While some experiences are considered to be bad customer service, often it is merely the customer\'s perception of the situation and inability to compromise that can turn a good customer service experience into a bad one.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][vc_custom_heading text="Open positions" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1495690320780{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}"][stm_vacancies text="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'meta' => array ( '_vc_post_settings' => array ( 0 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', ), '_edit_lock' => array ( 0 => '1501766274:1', ), '_edit_last' => array ( 0 => '1', ), '_wp_page_template' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), 'slide_template' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), '_wpb_vc_js_status' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), '_wpb_shortcodes_custom_css' => array ( 0 => '.vc_custom_1490675647650{margin-bottom: 39px !important;}.vc_custom_1495690320780{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}', ), 'page_title_breadcrumbs' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'page_title_box' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'page_title_box_align' => array ( 0 => 'left', ), 'page_title_box_title_size' => array ( 0 => 'h2', ), 'page_title_box_bg_color' => array ( 0 => 'rgb(92, 55, 62)', ), 'page_title_box_text_color' => array ( 0 => 'ffffff', ), 'page_title_box_line_color' => array ( 0 => 'ffffff', ), 'page_title_box_subtitle_color' => array ( 0 => 'ffffff', ), 'page_title_button_text' => array ( 0 => 'Get in touch', ), 'page_title_button_url' => array ( 0 => '/construction/contact-us', ), 'stm_sidebar_position' => array ( 0 => 'left', ), 'ampforwp-amp-on-off' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), ), );
$pearl_page_beauty["some-history"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][stm_sidebar sidebar="1064"][/vc_column][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-9 vc_col-md-9"][vc_single_image image="1076" img_size="full" css=".vc_custom_1495609320491{margin-bottom: 54px !important;}"][vc_column_text]For something as fun as makeup, it tends to be at the center of a lot of controversy. Women who choose to wear it are sometimes accused of “lying,” while others are viewed as lacking confidence. It’s a sad reality, but these kinds of accusations often shame ladies from layering on the foundation and mascara that might make them feel a bit better about themselves in the morning (or that they just straight-up love).[/vc_column_text][stm_company_history style="style_2"][stm_company_history_item year="2003" title="Goldy Sanders comes to New York" description="Today\'s salons are about more than just cutting hair. So when you are looking through a beauty salon supply catalog, website or showroom, there are some items you should consider that will put you a cut above your competition."][stm_company_history_item year="2005" title="She opens a small hair salon for little girls naming it Cinderella" description="One of the ways to look for cheap beauty salon equipment is to search for wholesale salon packages that offers a whole complete set of salon equipment at reasonable prices. Just be checking out these packages, you will be able to fully equip your beauty salon without have a big headache of searching everyone for one set of equipments to another."][stm_company_history_item year="2008" title="Cinderella becomes a popular place with reservation list" description="Beauty salon business is sprouting everywhere. It is not surprising that many people are engaging on this type business nowadays because starting a beauty salon has minimum requirements. Putting up a beauty salon or a spa treatment facility focuses on finding a suitable place and setting up efficient beauty equipments."][stm_company_history_item year="2012" title="Cinderella extends services range for grown-ups" description="The beauty industry is a business that is not gravely affected by any economic crisis. Naturally, women will purchase beauty products or use their money to make beauty improvements. The women need to be beautiful is also not influenced by their economic status."][stm_company_history_item year="2017" title="Cinderella wins the Award for ``The Best Beauty Salon``" description="Beauty is an ever booming business that will never see a lack in customers because women and even men will continue to go to beauty salons for a new hairdo, for a manicure, a pedicure or even a tan. So, whether there is a depression or not, women (and some men) will still go to beauty salons to have their fix. "][/stm_company_history][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'meta' => array ( '_vc_post_settings' => array ( 0 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', ), '_edit_lock' => array ( 0 => '1501765263:1', ), '_edit_last' => array ( 0 => '1', ), '_wp_page_template' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), 'slide_template' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), '_wpb_vc_js_status' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), '_wpb_shortcodes_custom_css' => array ( 0 => '.vc_custom_1495609320491{margin-bottom: 54px !important;}', ), 'page_title_breadcrumbs' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'page_title_box' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'page_title_box_align' => array ( 0 => 'left', ), 'page_title_box_title_size' => array ( 0 => 'h2', ), 'page_title_box_bg_color' => array ( 0 => 'rgb(92, 55, 62)', ), 'page_title_box_text_color' => array ( 0 => 'ffffff', ), 'page_title_box_line_color' => array ( 0 => 'ffffff', ), 'page_title_box_subtitle_color' => array ( 0 => 'ffffff', ), 'page_title_button_text' => array ( 0 => 'Get in touch', ), 'page_title_button_url' => array ( 0 => '/construction/contact-us', ), 'stm_sidebar_position' => array ( 0 => 'left', ), 'ampforwp-amp-on-off' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), ), );
