$pearl_page_beauty["service-1"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row css=".vc_custom_1502168086766{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-9 vc_col-md-9"][stm_carousel_gallery images_effect="0" thumbnails="disable" description="disable" pagination="disable" images="1207,1208" image_size="870x370"][vc_custom_heading text="Cuticle Removal" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left|color:%230a2045" use_theme_fonts="yes" type="theme_style"][vc_column_text]A <strong>Basic Manicure </strong>is designed for the individual that wants their nails cleaned, cut &amp; shaped, cuticles cleaned up, gentle buffing the nails for shine then to complete this service, a light hand and arm massage. A <strong>Basic Manicure with Polish</strong> contains all the above steps as the Basic Manicure except before the hand and arm massage, polish is applied. An <strong>Express Manicure</strong> contains all the steps as the Basic Manicure with polish but there is no massage, to complete this service a moisturizer is applied to the hand.[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1437394020523{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="7/12" css=".vc_custom_1437394032961{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="How our Nail Masters work" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left|color:%230a2045" use_theme_fonts="yes" type="theme_style" css=".vc_custom_1496819911549{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"][vc_column_text]Our signature manicure using formaldehyde-free, paraben-free lotions and polishes. This classic nail treatment shapes, buffs and gloss nails to perfection. Upgrade your Classic Mani and Pedi with a hydrating mask.[/vc_column_text][stm_iconlist icon="fa fa-check" iconsize="16"] <ul> <li>Sterilizing the tools and materials</li> <li>Applying high-quality cosmetic materials</li> <li>Using single-use handgloves and finger separators</li> <li>Keeping the track of schedule</li> <li>Maintaining accurate records</li> <li>Offering extra comfort for customers</li> </ul> [/stm_iconlist][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="5/12" css=".vc_custom_1437394029040{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="Latest Work" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left|color:%230a2045" use_theme_fonts="yes" type="theme_style" css=".vc_custom_1496819917231{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"][stm_carousel_gallery images_effect="0" autoscroll="disable" navigation="disable" thumbnails="disable" description="disable" pagination="disable" dots="enable" style="style_4" images="1209,1210,1211,1212,1213" image_size="345x260"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_custom_heading text="What is Included" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left|color:%230a2045" use_theme_fonts="yes" type="theme_style" css=".vc_custom_1496819926782{margin-top: 20px !important;margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"][vc_tta_accordion c_icon="triangle" active_section="1" color="white" c_position="right"][vc_tta_section title="Nail Care" tab_id="1436856364309-4693ae6d-d440"][vc_column_text]Nail care products not only help make your nails look beautiful but many of them are designed to help you care for your nails. It is important to remember that your nails need care to avoid disease and infection. Make time in your week to look after your nails and toe nails.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Hand Care" tab_id="1436856390578-b0750fdc-2914"][vc_column_text]You use your hands every single day and still, many people do not take the time to take care of their hands. In this article, we are going to touch base on 4 tips for effective hand care that will allow you to have soft skin and beautiful looking nails![/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Hygiene and Sanitation" tab_id="1436856406415-b8e38c00-5add"][vc_column_text]Washing hands with soap and water may not be possible when you are on the move. This is where sanitizing wipes come in handy.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][vc_custom_heading text="Book your visit online" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left|color:%230a2045" use_theme_fonts="yes" type="theme_style" css=".vc_custom_1496819932564{margin-top: 40px !important;margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"][stm_contact_form_7 form="1215"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][stm_sidebar sidebar="1064"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'meta' => array ( '_vc_post_settings' => array ( 0 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', 1 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', ), '_wpb_shortcodes_custom_css' => array ( 0 => '.vc_custom_1502168086766{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}.vc_custom_1437394020523{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}.vc_custom_1496819926782{margin-top: 20px !important;margin-bottom: 20px !important;}.vc_custom_1496819932564{margin-top: 40px !important;margin-bottom: 20px !important;}.vc_custom_1437394032961{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}.vc_custom_1437394029040{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}.vc_custom_1496819911549{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}.vc_custom_1496819917231{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}', 1 => '.vc_custom_1502168086766{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}.vc_custom_1437394020523{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}.vc_custom_1496819926782{margin-top: 20px !important;margin-bottom: 20px !important;}.vc_custom_1496819932564{margin-top: 40px !important;margin-bottom: 20px !important;}.vc_custom_1437394032961{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}.vc_custom_1437394029040{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}.vc_custom_1496819911549{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}.vc_custom_1496819917231{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}', ), '_edit_last' => array ( 0 => '1', ), '_wpb_vc_js_status' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'slide_template' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), 'page_bg_repeat' => array ( 0 => 'repeat', ), 'title' => array ( 0 => 'show', ), 'title_box_bg_color' => array ( 0 => '#0a1f44', ), 'title_box_font_color' => array ( 0 => '#ffffff', ), 'title_box_line_color' => array ( 0 => '#c41d54', ), 'title_box_custom_bg_image' => array ( 0 => '86'